Repeat Rate:
select count(distinct user_id) from dev_db.dbt_tomiasikainenkaitofi.fact_user_orders where frequent_buyer = true;
99 distinct users who have bought more than once

User likely to buy again are for example user who buys often a good spend:
select * 
from dev_db.dbt_tomiasikainenkaitofi.fact_orders
where orders > 5
and total_spend > 1000;

increasing spend canalso be a indicator for likelihood to buy again:
select user_id, created_at, order_total
from dev_db.dbt_tomiasikainenkaitofi.fact_user_orders
order by user_id,created_at desc;
